col10: This rule adds facades with architectural detail to a simple building mass. It's meant to be run on a closed volume, a closed multipatch in ArcGIS Pro or volumetric shape in CityEngine.
This rule classifies/colors the faces of a mass by their orientation.
A rule that creates a representation of the Taj Mahal purely from primitives available in Computer Generated Architecture (CGA).
This rule creates a 3D manhole, with realistic textures, that can be adjusted through parameters.
This rule applies a color to a shape or multipatch.
A rule to create a natural park area, with scattered trees.
A rule to create formal parks, with walking paths.
A procedural rule for creating wind turbines.
This rule creates a 3D representation of a camera's view.

This rule create an rail guideway, with retaining walls on both sides. If elevated off the ground it will automatically create pillars to support itself down to the elevation surface. You can control the thickness and frequency of the pillars with rule parameters. Height is control by manipulating the height of each graph segment. Note, this rule is meant to be used exclusively in CityEngine, not ArcGIS Pro.
This rule creates an elevated rail guideway, with the tracks below for a suspended train, and a green space above. It's meant to be used in CityEngine on the street portion of a graph.
A simple CGA rule that applies a color to a shape based on an attribute, in this case zoning.
A rule that creates zoning volumes on parcels, with street setbacks, maximum height, and colored by zoning type.
This rule creates a 3D cage around the outer edge of a shape or polygon.
This rule creates a 3D cage around a shape that can be used as a scalar for creating 3D objects.
This rule creates a 3D catch basin, with realistic textures, that can be adjusted through parameters.
This rule creates a 3D runway sign, with customizable text, that can be adjusted through parameters.
This rule creates a 3D storage tank that can be customized for shape and size through parameters.
This rule creates a 3D jetway model, that can be customized to fit different aircraft.
This rule creates a 3D wall sign, with a replaceable textures that can be adjusted through parameters.
